gov.usgs.volcanoes.core.util

Class ProgressInputStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.InputStream
      • gov.usgs.volcanoes.core.util.ProgressInputStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class ProgressInputStream
extends InputStream
implements Closeable
    Extension of InputStream, we provide expected stream length and this class calls registered progress listeners after every read event with read percentage.
    Version:
    $Id: ProgressInputStream.java,v 1.1 2007-04-24 21:37:03 dcervelli Exp $
    Author:
    Dan Cervelli
